  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"Fliese\"</strong> is an minimal logic puzzle game.<br><br>Your goal is to turn all the pieces on the board into a clear color, with each type of piece changing the board in their specific way. Play trough 120 levels of minimalist aesthetic relaxing meditation, unlocking new levels as you go.<br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>120 levels<br></li><li>Color Modes<br></li><li>Minimalistic<br></li><li>Relaxing<br></li><li>Simple<br></li><li>Meditative soundtrack</li></ul>",
